WEBVTT

00:01.869 --> 00:02.739
Tell me I'm beautiful.

00:03.682 --> 00:05.369
Tell me we'll grow old together.

00:05.921 --> 00:08.849
Tell me that I'm still the one.

00:09.597 --> 00:10.249
That you need me.

00:11.283 --> 00:12.989
That I'm your superhero.

00:14.287 --> 00:15.501
Tell me you'll never let me go.

00:16.385 --> 00:17.487
Tell me you miss me.

00:18.561 --> 00:19.547
Tell me you love me.

00:21.318 --> 00:22.456
It's all I want to hear.

00:23.578 --> 00:25.443
Everyone has something they need to hear.

00:25.935 --> 00:27.847
Vow to tell them this Valentine's Day.

